{{Unreferenced|date=July 2007}} {{Infobox company | name = AB Svenska Ord | logo = | caption = | type = | traded_as = | genre = <!-- Only used with media and publishing companies --> | fate = | predecessor = | successor = | foundation = {{Start date|1961||}} | founder = | defunct = <!-- {{End date|YYYY|MM|DD}} --> | location_city = | location_country = Sweden | location = | locations = | area_served = | key_people = | industry = | products = | services = | revenue = | operating_income = | net_income = | aum = <!-- Only used with financial services companies --> | assets = | equity = | owner = [[Hasse & Tage]] | num_employees = | parent = | divisions = | subsid = | homepage = <!-- {{URL|www.example.com}} --> | footnotes = | intl = }} '''AB Svenska Ord''' was a well-known entertainment company in [[Sweden]], run by comedy duo [[Hasse & Tage]]. It was established in 1961.
==Productions== Svenska Ord published a series of cabarets, films, and books, among them some of the following:
*1984 - ''Fröken Fleggmans mustasch'' ("The Mustache of Miss Fleggman") (TV-theatre) *1982 - ''[[The Simple-Minded Murder|Den Enfaldige Mördaren]] ("The Simple-Minded Murder")'' (film) *1981 - ''SOPOR'' ("GARBAGE") (film) *1980 - ''Under dubbelgöken'' (variety) (TV) *1978 - ''[[The Adventures of Picasso|Picassos äventyr]] (The Adventures of Picasso)'' (film) *1976 - ''[[Svea hund]]'' (variety) (TV) *1975 - ''Ägget är löst'' ("The egg is loose") (film) *1975 - ''[[Release the Prisoners to Spring|Släpp fångarne loss - det är vår!]] (Release the Prisoners to Spring)'' (film) *1973 - ''Glaset i örat'' ("The glass in the ear") (variety) (TV) *1972 - ''[[The Man Who Quit Smoking|Mannen som slutade röka]] (The man who Quit Smoking)'' (film) *1971 - ''[[The Apple War|Äppelkriget]]'' ("The Apple War") (film) *1970 - ''88-öresrevyn'' ("The 88-cent review") (variety) (TV) *1970 - ''[[Spader madame]]'' (TV) *1969 - ''[[Spader madame]]'' (variety; stage version) *1968 - ''Lådan'' ("The box (the drawer)") (variety) (TV) *1968 - ''I huvet på en gammal gubbe'' ("In the head of an old fellow") (film) *1965 - ''[[Docking the Boat|Att angöra en brygga]] (Docking the Boat)'' (film) *1964 - ''[[Swedish Portraits|Svenska bilder]] (Swedish Portraits)'' (film) *1964 - ''[[Yellow Dog (Variety)|Gula hund]]'' (Yellow Dog) (variety) (TV) *1963 - ''Hålligång'' (variety) (TV) *1962 - ''[[Gröna hund]]'' ("Green dog") (variety) *1959 - ''Doktor Kotte slår till eller Siv Olsson'' ("Dr. Kotte strikes again or Siv Olsson") (variety)
