'''Nehanda Radio''' is a [[Zimbabwe]]an online radio station that provides 24-hour updated news on Zimbabwe. The station is run by exiled journalist [[Lance Guma]].

The project also recently launched [[Nehanda TV]] which aims at promoting Zimbabwean videos.  This is important for the voice of democracy and freedom of information in emerging democracies such as Zimbabwe. Zimbabwe has harsh Media laws and projects like Nehanda Radio serve to keep Zimbabweans informed.{{citation needed|date=April 2015}}

